PRETORIA - The critically-acclaimed play, The Fall is running at The State Theatre in Pretoria. It is based on the University of Cape Town hashtag Rhodes Must Fall. READ: Some of the activists behind #RhodesMustFall campaign The production focuses on seven drama graduates who share their personal experiences of those times. *View the attached video where Tankiso Mamabolo and Sizwesandile Mnisi, who wrote and directed the play, give Weekend Wake Up insight into some of the characters. eNCA